window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Exciting 3rd Installment of Arcane Knight!</p> <p>The third installment of the Arcane Knight series is here, and things are heating up. Caldor and Warrick set off to explore the Southlands, but they soon find themselves caught in the midst of a brewing war between the Houses of Newalyn. Meanwhile, strange things are happening in the dungeons, and Caldor must stay true to his Oaths and promises as he navigates the dangerous political landscape.</p> <p>As the war rages on, Caldor finds himself thrust into a leadership role as a Knight and Vassal Lord of Blackridge keep. His loyalty is put to the test as he struggles to keep his men safe amidst the chaos of battle. But war has a way of changing a person, and Caldor will soon discover the true cost of conflict.</p> <p>The third installment of the Arcane Knight series offers a thrilling blend of adventure, politics, and action. With Caldor at the center of it all, readers will be hooked as they follow his journey through the dangers of war. Will he be able to emerge from the conflict unscathed, or will he be forever changed by the brutality of battle? Find out in this exciting new book.</p> <p>This LitRPG adventure novel offers an immersive world filled with levels, stats, and cool abilities. With no Harem, loads of fun violence, and a dash of politics, listeners will be captivated by Caldor's journey to achieve his dreams.</p>"; 
